      <item>
        <title>Stricken City</title>
        <link>https://meorion.github.io/blog/20220629/</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jun 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://meorion.github.io/blog/20220629/</guid>
        <description>I wanted to see. I wanted to be there. That far off there. The perptually perfect. Something to behold. Not now. No time. Today was the day the world would end. Their world. He would see it. His world, of course would go on. Some of them would go on, too. but not as they know it. Not as they have known it.
Dusty. Windy. Desolate. a glint of reflection. something reflecting.</description>
      </item>
      
